    "content": ". | Connect a micro USB cable to the UART-USB port J5 | For programming, connect a micro USB cable to the USB Debug port J19 | Use the micro sdcard slot J10 of the device to insert a micro sdcard | . ",
    "url": "http://localhost:4000/bootloader_apps_sdcard/apps/sdcard_bootloader/docs/readme_pic32mz_das_sk.html#setting-up-pic32mz-embedded-graphics-with-stacked-dram-da-starter-kit-crypto",
